### Update a space

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.space/v3/spaces/[guid]" \
  -X PATCH \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{ "name": "new-space-name" }'

```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

<%= yield_content :space %>
```

#### Definition
`PATCH /v3/spaces/:guid`

#### Optional Parameters

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
**name** | _string_ | New space name |
**metadata.labels** _(experimental)_| [_label object_](#labels) | Labels applied to the space.
**metadata.annotations** _(experimental)_| [_annotation object_](#annotations) | Annotations applied to the space.

